      "span_text": "Since δ-invariant σ-traces on D H are precisely the 0-cocycles in the Hopf-cyclic cohomology HC • H (D H, σ k δ ), we are motivated to define more generally the n-dimensional closed graded (H, M )-traces on a DGH-category S H (see, Definition 5."
